@node "SESysDatTextWHO" "Text WHO"


                     @{b}SystemEditor (System Datas): Text WHO
                    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Use an mci text file instead of internal who.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SESysDatMultiNodeUser" "MultiNodeUser"


                  @{b}SystemEditor (System Datas): MultiNodeUser
                 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Let the same user login to different nodes at the same time.

@endnode

