@node "SESysDatRightFilenames" "Right Filenames"


                 @{b}SystemEditor (System Datas): Right Filenames
                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Format file names to right positions at file listings.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SESysDatMsgCryPWMsgHeader" "MsgCryPW MsgHeader"


                @{b}SystemEditor (System Datas): MsgCryPW MsgHeader
               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Use as default 'File Crypt PW' for crypting messages.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SESysDatAutoRestrict" "Auto Restrict"


                   @{b}SystemEditor (System Datas): Auto Restrict
                  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

FAME will automatically set on all data files it creates the file comment 
'RESTRICTED'.

With 'RESTRICTED' downloading of a 'RESTRICTED' file isn't possible from FAME
and some doors.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SESysDatFileCryPWFileList" "FileCryPW FileList"


                @{b}SystemEditor (System Datas): FileCryPW FileList
               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Use as default 'File Crypt PW' for crypting filelists.

