@node "SETextLangType1to15" "Text Lang. Type 1 - 15"


              @{b}SystemEditor (Text Language): Text Lang. Type 1 - 15
             ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Type here 1 to 15 different languages.
The languages will be used for user-locale.


Examples and the first time from the SystemEditor generated:

 1: english
 2: deutsch
 3: dansk
 4: espa±ol
 5: franńais
 6: italiano
 7: nederlands
 8: norsk
 9: portuguĻs
10: svenska
11:


Note: The first free gadget indicates the end of the Text Lang. Types.
      In this case 11 is free so FAME uses Text Lang. Types from 1 to 10.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SETextLangExt1to15" "Extension 1 - 15"


                 @{b}SystemEditor (Text Language): Extension 1 - 15
                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Type here 1 to 15 different Extensions.
The Extensions will be used for textfile Extensions to have textfiles in
different languages/ansis.


Examples and the first time from the SystemEditor generated:

