@node "SEDPortNamXIMDoorPort" "XIMDoorPort"


                  @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): XIMDoorPort
                 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The XIMDoorPort name for XIM door emulation.

Default: 'XIMDoorPort'

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SEDPortNamTIMDoorPort" "TIMDoorPort"


                  @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): TIMDoorPort
                 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The TIMDoorPort name for TIM (paragon) door emulation.

Default: 'DoorControl'

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SEDPortNamRexxDoorPort" "RexxDoorPort"


                  @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): RexxDoorPort
                 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The RexxDoorPort name for the Nodes Arexx-Ports.

Default: 'FAMERexxPort.'

Note: The Nodenumber will be added to the port name !

      Examples: - FAMERexxPort.<x>     <x> = Nodenumber
                - FAMERexxPort.1         1 = Node 1

Note: There is no need to change this port name.
      It's recommended to leave the default name.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SEDPortNamServerDoorPort" "ServerDoorPort"


                 @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): ServerDoorPort
                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The ServerDoorPort name is used by the Nodes @{"(MainPart)" link "MainPart.guide/Main"} and the @{"Server" link "Server.guide/Main"}.

Default: 'FAMEServerPort'

Note: You can't change it and this is good as it is, because else FAME will
      be no longer able to run.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SEDPortNamToolPort" "ToolPort"


                    @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): ToolPort
                   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The ToolPort name is used for the ToolPort of the @{"Server" link "Server.guide/Main"}.

Default: 'FAMEToolPort'

Note: There is no need to change this port name.
      It's recommended to leave the default name.

@endnode

